"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-life-style-noah-lyles-girlfriend-junelle-bromfield-olympics-b2592832.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  The Olympic track and field athlete met his girlfriend in 2017, five years before they started officially dating  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 411, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Team USA's gold medalist track and field sprinter,Noah Lyles, finished first by five-thousandths of a second in the Paris 2024 Olympics 100m final on August 4.\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 436, \"end\": 444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"score\": 0.9845152108726851, \"rank\": 0.00797968093448017, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_national_team\"}, {\"begin\": 486, \"end\": 496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old athlete's photo-finish outcome was celebrated, positioning him well to become the first American man to win gold in the 100m and 200m races since Carl Lewis in 1984.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 777, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999836114713226, \"rank\": 1.4244249189031466e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carl Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the wake of Lyles' triumph, ahead of the August 8 200m race, his girlfriend, Junelle Bromfield,took to her social mediato honor him and his accomplishment.\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 794, \"end\": 799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9973904368487968, \"rank\": 0.00257051980920836, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 859, \"end\": 876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Junelle_Bromfield\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Junelle Bromfield\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Junelle_Bromfield\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Junelle_Bromfield\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The double is alive,\\\" she wrote, insinuating Lyles could make history if he wins the 200m final.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 984, \"end\": 989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9973904368487968, \"rank\": 0.00257051980920836, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bromfield, an Olympic track athlete for TeamJamaica, has been linked to Lyles for years.\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"score\": 0.9989483383467707, \"rank\": 0.001052726003029814, \"text\": \"Bromfield\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\"}, {\"begin\": 1109, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9973904368487968, \"rank\": 0.00257051980920836, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair met through social media in 2017, pursuing a romantic relationship.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, nothing came of their first date, according to Lyles.\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1259, \"end\": 1264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9973904368487968, \"rank\": 0.00257051980920836, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't until five years later that the duo gave their romance another shot, and it stuck.\", \"from\": 1266, \"to\": 1358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, the power couple is supporting each other on their track for gold at theParis 2024 games.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And already, Lyles and Bromfield will not be returning home empty-handed.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1468, \"end\": 1473, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.997390