apshot at the Night of Legends event.\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 26-year-old athlete first attended the Olympics in 2021 for the Tokyo Games.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There, she finished third in the 4x400m relay race, winning her first Olympic bronze medal.\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since the last summer series, Bromfield has been training alongside Lyles.\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2671, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2627, \"end\": 2636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"score\": 0.9989483383467707, \"rank\": 0.001052726003029814, \"text\": \"Bromfield\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\"}, {\"begin\": 2665, \"end\": 2670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9973904368487968, \"rank\": 0.00257051980920836, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, she's set to compete in the 4x400m relay race again, the women's 400m on August 9, and possibly the 400m final on August 10.\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2807, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the past two years, living with Lyles in Florida, Bromfield has grown quite close to his family, especially his mom Keisha Caine.\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2845, \"end\": 2850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9973904368487968, \"rank\": 0.00257051980920836, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 2854, \"end\": 2861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"score\": 0.9825400867897887, \"rank\": 0.017553296187961757, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\"}, {\"begin\": 2863, \"end\": 2872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"score\": 0.9989483383467707, \"rank\": 0.001052726003029814, \"text\": \"Bromfield\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\"}, {\"begin\": 2929, \"end\": 2935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keisha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keisha_Buchanan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In conversation withThe Inside Lanein early July, Bromfield confessed Caine has been majorly helpful in her Florida transition and Olympic training.\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 3091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2993, \"end\": 3002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"score\": 0.9989483383467707, \"rank\": 0.001052726003029814, \"text\": \"Bromfield\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\"}, {\"begin\": 3051, \"end\": 3058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"score\": 0.9825400867897887, \"rank\": 0.017553296187961757, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"I want to give a big shout-out to my boyfriend and his mom because when I went to Florida, I wasn't driving, and she took me to training and back every day, which was like 40 minutes.\", \"from\": 3093, \"to\": 3287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3186, \"end\": 3193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"score\": 0.9825400867897887, \"rank\": 0.017553296187961757, \"text\": \"Florida\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Florida\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's a support that I am extremely grateful for.\\\"\", \"from\": 3288, \"to\": 3339, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While Bromfield has formed a close connection with Lyles' family, Lyles has visited Bromfield's loved ones in Jamaica.\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3347, \"end\": 3356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"score\": 0.9989483383467707, \"rank\": 0.001052726003029814, \"text\": \"Bromfield\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\"}, {\"begin\": 3392, \"end\": 3397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9973904368487968, \"rank\": 0.00257051980920836, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 3407, \"end\": 3412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9973904368487968, \"rank\": 0.00257051980920836, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 3425, \"end\": 3434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"score\": 0.9989483383467707, \"rank\": 0.001052726003029814, \"text\": \"Bromfield\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\"}, {\"begin\": 3451, \"end\": 3458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999993369784, \"rank\": 6.618572102195225e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you go to Jamaica, you are treated like a freaking rock star,\\\"the gold medalist recalled during a 2024 press conferenceahead of the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3618, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3476, \"end\": 3483, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"score\": 0.9999999993369784, \"rank\": 6.618572102195225e-10, \"text\": \"Jamaica\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the two years they have been together, Lyles' mental health advocacy has influenced Bromfield to take major steps in her own journey.\", \"from\": 3620, \"to\": 3756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3662, \"end\": 3667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9973904368487968, \"rank\": 0.00257051980920836, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 3707, \"end\": 3716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"score\": 0.9989483383467707, \"rank\": 0.001052726003029814, \"text\": \"Bromfield\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles has openly talked about his use of prescribed antidepressants since 2020, encouraging others to find solace in his personal story and strength in his continued drive - something Bromfield's been able to do.\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 3969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3941, \"end\": 3950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"score\": 0.9989483383467707, \"rank\": 0.001052726003029814, \"text\": \"Bromfield\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I started therapy about two years ago because my boyfriend is big on therapy and felt I needed it,\\\" she toldThe Inside Lane.\", \"from\": 3971, \"to\": 4096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been really helpful because I have been dealing with survivor's guilt, which was weighing on me.\", \"from\": 4097, \"to\": 4199, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, I feel like I can live my life fully and enjoy every moment because life is short.\\\"\", \"from\": 4200, \"to\": 4288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Bromfield's influence, Lyles toldInside Trackthat his relationship has made him more patient.\", \"from\": 4290, \"to\": 4386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4293, \"end\": 4302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"score\": 0.9989483383467707, \"rank\": 0.001052726003029814, \"text\": \"Bromfield\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lordship_of_Bromfield_and_Yale\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It has taught me a lot of patience and I believe this is my best relationship ever,\\\" he said during the March recording.\", \"from\": 4387, \"to\": 4508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The two have ensured their professional lives remain separate from their relationship.\", \"from\": 4510, \"to\": 4596, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They may train together, but when it comes time for their track meets, they act like acquaintances with their game face on.\", \"from\": 4597, \"to\": 4720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She will not even let me call her 'baby' at practice,\\\" Lyles said on theFast Lane Lifestylepodcast.\", \"from\": 4722, \"to\": 4822, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4824, \"to\": 5054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4875, \"end\": 4886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.460570615847991e-15, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"